<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 18:11:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列战争第333天：消息人士告诉CNN，内塔尼亚胡“鱼雷”破坏了停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</link><description>消息人士告诉美国有线电视新闻网，内塔尼亚胡宣布以色列永远不会离开费城走廊，从而“破坏”了恢复人质释放谈判的努力。 10 月 7 日，战争可能导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令 ■ 这是战争开始 333 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长和政界人士参加欢乐婚礼，被谋杀的人质安息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-politicians-attend-joyous-wedding-as-murdered-hostages-laid-to-rest/00000191-b84d-d95b-a1d5-b97d2f830000</link><description>该活动的视频在社交媒体上广泛传播，联盟成员微笑、欢呼、跳舞庆祝。婚礼与赫什·戈德堡-波林和卡梅尔·盖特的葬礼在同一天举行</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-politicians-attend-joyous-wedding-as-murdered-hostages-laid-to-rest/00000191-b84d-d95b-a1d5-b97d2f830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇提议对2025年预算采取严格的财务措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</link><description>这位极右翼部长说，我们正处于战争之中，但我们将在经济战线上共同获胜。拟议的措施包括冻结所得税等级、冻结公共部门工资、冻结最低工资以及取消游客增值税豁免。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:12:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</guid></item><item><title>两名西岸定居者因袭击阿拉伯以色列妇女而被起诉；一名被指控犯有恐怖罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</link><description>来自约旦河西岸定居点的两名男子被指控犯有出于种族动机的罪行，其中一名男子在袭击了来自贝都因市拉哈特的四名妇女和一名幼儿后，还被指控犯有恐怖主义罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡发表了一番激动人心、夸夸其谈的演讲，终结了人质协议的希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</link><description>在首次向人质家属请求宽恕后，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡又回到了自己的本性：连续撒谎，无视令人不快的事实，并承诺以牺牲协议为代价留在费城路线上。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列烧焦的北部能否从真主党导弹袭击的废墟中崛起？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-09-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israels-scorched-north-rise-from-the-ashes-of-hezbollahs-missiles-attacks/00000191-b74e-db99-a1d1-bf7e62610000</link><description>战争期间，加利利和戈兰高地的大片自然区域被点燃，其中包括以色列一些最受欢迎且曾经是田园诗般的景点。乘坐专为此目的制造的车辆进入一片烧焦的土地</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-09-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israels-scorched-north-rise-from-the-ashes-of-hezbollahs-missiles-attacks/00000191-b74e-db99-a1d1-bf7e62610000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争目标、撤离人员和费城：以色列总理内塔尼亚胡的事实核查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，内塔尼亚胡总理就一些关键问题提出了许多主张。然而，仔细观察就会发现，内塔尼亚胡并不像他表面上表现的那么诚实，他在以色列的战争目标、费城路线等问题上反复无常。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 13:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队预备役人员袭击为援助组织工作的加沙卡车司机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</link><description>巴勒斯坦司机接受了以色列安全部门的筛查，与哈马斯或其他恐怖组织没有联系。以色列国防军士兵个人反对援助物资进入加沙地带，他们在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点加沙一侧殴打、戴上手铐并蒙住他们的眼睛。截至本报告发布，无人受到质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和犹太领导人谴责英国暂停向以色列转让部分武器的“可耻”决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡说：“英国的错误决定只会让哈马斯更加嚣张。”英国首席拉比谴责部分武器暂停是“乞丐的信仰”</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列重新占领加沙，“神圣”的费城路线将由人质尸体铺成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们知道，军队在加沙和埃及边境的存在过去并没有阻止哈马斯的袭击。其目标实际上是让以色列永远留在加沙，这个目标不再是愚蠢的，而是邪恶的</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列西岸攻势加剧，简易爆炸物成为主要挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</link><description>约旦河西岸北部的大规模行动对巴勒斯坦难民营造成严重破坏，以色列军队努力“剥落”路面以发现埋设的爆炸物</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民部长出访行程曝光：大多与极右翼领导人会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-ministers-travel-itinerary-revealed-mostly-visits-to-far-right-leaders/00000191-b2dd-db99-a1d1-bfffe4700000</link><description>这位侨民部长 2024 年初的旅行计划包括与法国、西班牙和波兰的极右翼政党领导人会面，以色列与这些国家没有正式关系；文件显示，此次旅行花费约 500,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:51:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-ministers-travel-itinerary-revealed-mostly-visits-to-far-right-leaders/00000191-b2dd-db99-a1d1-bfffe4700000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在被谋杀几天后播放了以色列人质伊登·耶鲁沙米在加沙被囚禁的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-eden-yerushalmi-in-gaza-captivity-days-after-murder/00000191-b67f-d9c6-a997-be7f05b10000</link><description>24 岁的 Yerushalmi 来自特拉维夫，于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 狂欢节上被绑架。预计她将在协议的最初人道主义阶段获释，本周早些时候，她的尸体与其他五名人质一起被归还</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:27:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-eden-yerushalmi-in-gaza-captivity-days-after-murder/00000191-b67f-d9c6-a997-be7f05b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员：10月7日不启动调查可能会导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、Gallant发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-refusal-to-appoint-oct-7-inquiry-increases-risk-of-icc-arrest-warrants/00000191-b5aa-dc3b-a7df-f7fabd4e0000</link><description>司法部消息人士称，政府拒绝总检察长关于成立国家调查委员会的建议，增加了检方请求获得批准的可能性。与此同时，以色列也得到了多个国家、组织和学术界对其立场的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-refusal-to-appoint-oct-7-inquiry-increases-risk-of-icc-arrest-warrants/00000191-b5aa-dc3b-a7df-f7fabd4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列怒火中烧，内塔尼亚胡编造谎言并判处人质死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-gaza-map-failed-to-show-the-route-he-used-to-funnel-qatari-cash-to-hamas/00000191-b46f-dc3b-a7df-f77f9c820000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡以安全担忧来掩盖自己的动机，主要是为了保护自己的政治地位。他正在努力维持他的联盟，如果加沙协议获得通过，这个联盟可能会瓦解</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-gaza-map-failed-to-show-the-route-he-used-to-funnel-qatari-cash-to-hamas/00000191-b46f-dc3b-a7df-f77f9c820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡发表声明前几个小时：以色列官员提出从费城撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article-live/netanyahu-nixes-key-part-of-u-s-led-gaza-plan-hamas-releases-video-of-murdered-hostage/00000191-b5c7-dd1b-a7db-b7df5fc60000</link><description>消息人士告诉CNN，内塔尼亚胡承诺永远不会让费城“鱼雷”人质谈判被破坏 ■ 内塔尼亚胡否决了美国领导的加沙计划的关键部分；哈马斯发布被谋杀人质的视频 ■ 欧洲汉莎航空集团航空公司恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article-live/netanyahu-nixes-key-part-of-u-s-led-gaza-plan-hamas-releases-video-of-murdered-hostage/00000191-b5c7-dd1b-a7db-b7df5fc60000</guid></item><item><title>新纪录片将曝光内塔尼亚胡腐败审讯的前所未见的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/u-s-documentary-to-show-unseen-leaked-footage-of-netanyahus-police-interrogation/00000191-b4bf-dc3b-a7df-f7ff167e0000</link><description>制片人亚历克斯·吉布尼表示，《比比档案》将于下周在多伦多电影节首映，并提供“其贪污腐败性格的有力证据”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 22:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/u-s-documentary-to-show-unseen-leaked-footage-of-netanyahus-police-interrogation/00000191-b4bf-dc3b-a7df-f7ff167e0000</guid></item><item><title>法官释放18名停火抗议者；以色列警方称“一定程度”要求对他们进行审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/judge-releases-18-tel-aviv-protesters-police-say-certain-levels-demand-they-be-tried/00000191-b461-dc3b-a7df-f771f4d30000</link><description>一名警方代表承认，大规模人质抗议活动被认为“非常具有侵略性”。法官注意到对被拘留者不利的证据很少，其中一人没有出示任何证据</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 20:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/judge-releases-18-tel-aviv-protesters-police-say-certain-levels-demand-they-be-tried/00000191-b461-dc3b-a7df-f771f4d30000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不会停止”：数万名以色列人在愤怒的第三天抗议人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/were-not-stopping-tens-of-thousands-demand-hostage-deal-on-third-day-of-rage-protests/00000191-b403-d95b-a1d5-bd3f47760000</link><description>在特拉维夫、耶路撒冷和其他城市，以色列人周一继续要求达成人质协议和停火。警方与内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷住所外的抗议者发生冲突，强行逮捕了几名抗议者</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 19:50:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/were-not-stopping-tens-of-thousands-demand-hostage-deal-on-third-day-of-rage-protests/00000191-b403-d95b-a1d5-bd3f47760000</guid></item><item><title>赫什的家人值得拜登、哈里斯和特朗普的思念和祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</link><description>如果美国立法者和官员真的想向赫什·戈德堡-波林、乔恩和雷切尔致敬，他们就必须公开呼吁达成一项能够确保赫什活着回家的协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</guid></item></channel></rss>